<!---------------------------

                  MERCENARIES

                  What TYPE of Merc is your character?
                    – Stand-Alone
                    – Hired Gun
                    – Parallel
                    – Narcissist

                  ABOUT THE TYPES
                  NOTE — They all have their own agendas which is their
                          primary similarity

                    Stand-Alone (SA)
                      • Doesn't care much for what other people have on their to-do list
                      • They are capable of a variety of jobs
                      • Potentially be an enemy to one or all of the organizations.

                    Hired Gun (HG)
                      • Will take job offers should they find one being tossed at them
                        ► Will take the job so long as the price is  right
                      • IF they are to align with or be a recurring hire for an 
                         organization, the org.'s opposition is not guaranteed to
                         become their own

                    Parallel (P)
                      • Will ally with an organization or group of people who hold 
                         similar beliefs as their own
                      • Take on the enemies of their allies as if they were their own

                    Narcissist (N)
                      • Believes their agenda is the only one that matters
                      • Will use anyone and anything, including mutliple organizations,
                         to achieve their goals
                      • Gladly hop between allies and make a number of enemies with
                         no regard for who they hurt along the way

---------------------------->

